DL-AMR Multi-License Notice
============================

This repository contains components distributed under different licenses,
reflecting the licensing requirements of the upstream projects on which
they depend. See individual LICENSE files for full text.

| Component                               | License                  | File                  |
|-----------------------------------------|--------------------------|-----------------------|
| Python training and analysis code       | MIT                      | LICENSE-CODE          |
| OpenFOAM solver modifications           | GNU GPL v3.0             | solver/LICENSE        |
| Pretrained model weights                | CC-BY 4.0                | LICENSE-DATA          |
| Reference data (CSVs, npz, etc.)        | CC-BY 4.0                | LICENSE-DATA          |
| Documentation and figures               | CC-BY 4.0                | LICENSE-DATA          |

Rationale:
- The OpenFOAM solver modifications (solver/) are derivative works of OpenFOAM,
  which is licensed under GNU GPL v3.0. Per the GPL v3.0 terms, these
  modifications are also distributed under GPL v3.0.
- Other code (Python training, analysis, scripts) is original work under MIT.
- Data artifacts (model weights, CSV/npz reference data) are under CC-BY 4.0
  to permit broad reuse with attribution.

